race.comment: READY TO RUSH (9) nice win on debut, before taking good ground off the speedy Ghielmi when second over 1000m at the Sapphire Coast. That form looks strong and no shock to see her go one better. MADE EASY (4) won with plenty up the sleeve on debut when taken to the front at Wagga over 1200m.  Will sit on the hot tempo and figure prominently. GANDALF (2) back in class and can stalk the good tempo after missing the jump when a disappointing sixth over 1100m at Hawkesbury. Each way. PAPARAZZO (5) indicated a win was imminent when launching late with the 61kg for a gritty second over 1112m at Kilmore. Blinkers go on and will be strong through the line.
